locality: Path to Heuningvleti, 2nd hill after turnoff. E slope substrate sandy.
Pakhuis Pass soil clayey Waboomveld, more than 6 years old cover 50%, height 80-120 cm.
Toekoms. N slope rock cover 20% vegetation cover 30% (50% of which restionaceae and Cyperaceae); height 80 cm; burnt two years ago.
Rooihoogte, 8 km N Villiersdorp. NNW slope roadside.
